description:
Welcome to a new theme at ChaosMen!
Not sure how often I will be airing them, but they will not replace regularly scheduled videos. just something extra to keep you guys busy at home!
My main goal for these vids is to capture a more intimate setting for new models, random models, and of course, my team that I already have on board.
First up is Dom who shares some time in his bathroom with us.
Enjoy!
